<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Action Required: Your recent payment failed</title>
<style>
  /* Reset & Base Styles */
  body, table, td, a {
    -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
    -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
  }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: #f4f7f6;
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #333333;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }
  /* Layout */
  .email-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    background-color: #f4f7f6;
    padding: 40px 0;
  }
  .email-content {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .email-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 30px 40px 10px;
  }
  .email-body {
    padding: 20px 40px 30px;
  }
  /* Typography */
  h1 {
    font-size: 22px;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #4a4a4a;
  }
  /* Highlight Box */
  .discount-box {
    background-color: #f0f7ff;
    border: 2px dashed #0066cc;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 25px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 30px 0;
  }
  .discount-box p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #004499;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .discount-code {
    display: block;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: bold;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    margin-top: 10px;
    color: #0066cc;
  }
  /* Button */
  .cta-container {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 35px 0 20px;
  }
  .cta-button {
    background-color: #0066cc;
    color: #ffffff !important;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: bold;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  /* Footer */
  .email-footer {
    background-color: #f9fafc;
    padding: 30px 40px;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
  }
  .email-footer p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #888888;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  /* Responsive */
  @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
    .email-body, .email-header, .email-footer {
      padding-left: 20px !important;
      padding-right: 20px !important;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="email-wrapper">
  <div class="email-content">

    <div class="email-body">
      <h1>Action Required: Your payment failed</h1>

      <p>Hi {{ $('Stripe Event Trigger').item.json.data.object.last_payment_error.payment_method.billing_details.name }},</p>

      <p>It looks like we ran into a small hiccup while processing your recent payment. Don't worry—this usually just happens due to an expired card, a typo, or a strict bank filter.</p>

      <p>To help get things back on track and make up for the inconvenience, we’ve set up a custom <strong>5% discount</strong> for you to apply when you retry your payment.</p>

      <div class="discount-box">
        <p>Use this promo code at checkout:</p>
        <span class="discount-code">{{ $json.id }}</span>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-container">
        <a href="https://www.blankarray.com/" class="cta-button">Update Payment Details</a>
      </div>

      <p>If you run into any issues or have questions, simply reply directly to this email and our support team will get it sorted out for you.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>
      <strong>The Blankarray Team</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>You are receiving this email because you recently attempted a transaction at blankarray.</p>
      <p>&copy; 2026 Blankarray. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>

